      <description>&lt;h3 id=&#34;容器安装和运行&#34;&gt;容器安装和运行&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;codeblock&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;        &lt;div class=&#34;copy-button-box&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;            &lt;button class=&#34;copy-button&#34; state=&#34;copy&#34; data=&#34;docker%20run%20-d%20%5c%0d%0a%20%20--name%20homeassistant%20%5c%0d%0a%20%20--privileged%20%5c%0d%0a%20%20--restart=unless-stopped%20%5c%0d%0a%20%20-e%20TZ=MY_TIME_ZONE%20%5c%0d%0a%20%20-v%20/PATH_TO_YOUR_CONFIG:/config%20%5c%0d%0a%20%20-v%20/run/dbus:/run/dbus:ro%20%5c%0d%0a%20%20--network=host%20%5c%0d%0a%20%20ghcr.io/home-assistant/home-assistant:stable&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;                &lt;i class=&#34;bi bi-copy&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xD;&#xA;            &lt;/button&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;        &lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34; data-lang=&#34;shell&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;docker run -d &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;\&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;  --name homeassistant &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;\&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;  --privileged &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;\&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;  --restart&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;unless-stopped &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;\&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;  -e TZ&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;MY_TIME_ZONE &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;\&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;  -v /PATH_TO_YOUR_CONFIG:/config &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;\&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;  -v /run/dbus:/run/dbus:ro &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;\&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;  --network&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;host &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;\&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;  ghcr.io/home-assistant/home-assistant:stable&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;更新镜像&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;codeblock&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;        &lt;div class=&#34;copy-button-box&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;            &lt;button class=&#34;copy-button&#34; state=&#34;copy&#34; data=&#34;#%20if%20this%20returns%20%22Image%20is%20up%20to%20date%22%20then%20you%20can%20stop%20here%0d%0adocker%20pull%20ghcr.io/home-assistant/home-assistant:stable%0d%0a%0d%0a#%20stop%20the%20running%20container%0d%0adocker%20stop%20homeassistant%0d%0a%0d%0a#%20remove%20it%20from%20Docker%27s%20list%20of%20containers%0d%0adocker%20rm%20homeassistant%0d%0a%0d%0a#%20finally,%20start%20a%20new%20one%0d%0adocker%20run%20-d%20%5c%0d%0a%20%20--name%20homeassistant%20%5c%0d%0a%20%20--restart=unless-stopped%20%5c%0d%0a%20%20--privileged%20%5c%0d%0a%20%20-e%20TZ=MY_TIME_ZONE%20%5c%0d%0a%20%20-v%20/PATH_TO_YOUR_CONFIG:/config%20%5c%0d%0a%20%20-v%20/run/dbus:/run/dbus:ro%20%5c%0d%0a%20%20--network=host%20%5c%0d%0a%20%20ghcr.io/home-assistant/home-assistant:stable&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;                &lt;i class=&#34;bi bi-copy&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xD;&#xA;            &lt;/button&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;        &lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;# if this returns &amp;#34;Image is up to date&amp;#34; then you can stop here&#xD;&#xA;docker pull ghcr.io/home-assistant/home-assistant:stable&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;# stop the running container&#xD;&#xA;docker stop homeassistant&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;# remove it from Docker&amp;#39;s list of containers&#xD;&#xA;docker rm homeassistant&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;# finally, start a new one&#xD;&#xA;docker run -d \&#xD;&#xA;  --name homeassistant \&#xD;&#xA;  --restart=unless-stopped \&#xD;&#xA;  --privileged \&#xD;&#xA;  -e TZ=MY_TIME_ZONE \&#xD;&#xA;  -v /PATH_TO_YOUR_CONFIG:/config \&#xD;&#xA;  -v /run/dbus:/run/dbus:ro \&#xD;&#xA;  --network=host \&#xD;&#xA;  ghcr.io/home-assistant/home-assistant:stable&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;docker run -d &lt;br&gt;&#xA;&amp;ndash;name homeassistant &lt;br&gt;&#xA;&amp;ndash;privileged &lt;br&gt;&#xA;&amp;ndash;restart=unless-stopped &lt;br&gt;&#xA;-e TZ=MY_TIME_ZONE &lt;br&gt;&#xA;-v /root/homeassistant/config:/config &lt;br&gt;&#xA;-v /run/dbus:/run/dbus:ro &lt;br&gt;&#xA;&amp;ndash;network=host &lt;br&gt;&#xA;c1eff36acdd7&lt;/p&gt;</description>
